      "![Page 1, Figure 2](subjects/Ggo/T3. AlineaciÃ³n de negocio y SI_TI. Bedell/Methodology_for_Business_Value_Analysis_of_Innovative_IT_in_a_Business_Sector._The_Case_of_the_Material_Supply_Chain-images/Methodology_for_Business_Value_Analysis_of_Innovative_IT_in_a_Business_Sector._The_Case_of_the_Material_Supply_Chain_page_001_img_001.png)",
