      "### Page 25",
      "Overview",
      "â€¢ NATS persistence engine",
      "â€¢ Messages can be stored and replayed at a later time",
      "â€¢ In a cluster of NATS servers, data can be replicated",
      "â€¢ Key Value store can be built on top",
      "â€¢ Object Store can be built on top",
      "â€¢ Late arriving consumers can still receive messages",
