      "### Page 26",
      "Streams",
      "â€¢ Stream == Named and ordered message store",
      "â€¢ Defines means of storage",
      "â€¢ Imposes limits",
      "â€¢ In memory",
      "â€¢ In File",
      "â€¢ Degree of replication (1 .. 5) among servers",
