      "â€¢ Normal subscribers cannot access the stream",
      "â€¢ Only new messages",
      "![Page 32, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_032.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 33",
      "Example",
      "â€¢ Create a consumer",
      "â€¢ nats consumer add",
      "â€¢ Set the name: marvel",
      "â€¢ Subscribe",
      "â€¢ nats consumer next sogreat marvel â€“count 100",
      "â€¢ We can see we are retrieving the messages we sent",
      "â€¢ Accept the defaults",
      "â€¢ nats consumer next sogreat marvel â€“count 100",
      "â€¢ No new messages appear",
      "![Page 33, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_033.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 34",
      "Example",
      "â€¢ We can replay: creating another consumer",
      "â€¢ nats consumer add â€¦",
      "â€¢ Or removing old consumer and recreating it",
      "â€¢ Clean up",
      "â€¢ nats stream purge sogreat",
      "â€¢ nats stream rm sogreat",
      "â€¢ nats consumer rm marvel",
      "â€¢ nats consumer add â€¦",
      "![Page 34, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_034.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 35",
      "Key Value Store",
      "â€¢ Built on top of Jetstream",
      "â€¢ Builds an immediately consistent map",
      "â€¢ A KV bucket corresponds to a stream",
      "â€¢ Operations on a bucket",
      "â€¢ put associates a value with a key",
      "â€¢ get retrieves the value associated with a key",
      "â€¢ delete remove any value associated with a key",
      "â€¢ purge remove all values associated with all keys",
      "â€¢ keys get all the keys with the operations associated",
      "![Page 35, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_035.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 36",
      "KV Store: concurrency control",
      "â€¢ Operations that verify a condition and mutate atomically",
      "â€¢ create associates a value with a key",
      "â€¢ update compare and set the value for a key",
      "â€¢ Only if the key does not exist",
      "â€¢ Fails if the revision provided is not the current one for the key",
      "![Page 36, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_036.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 37",
      "KV Store: stream operations",
      "â€¢ Getting streams",
      "â€¢ watch receives changes for a key (with wildcards)",
      "â€¢ watch all receive changes for all the keys in the bucket",
      "â€¢ Similar to a subscription",
      "â€¢ history list of the values and deletes for each key over time",
      "â€¢ By default, history of buckets set to 1.",
      "â€¢ Only the latest value/operation is stored",
      "![Page 37, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_037.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 38",
      "Example",
      "â€¢ Creating a KV Bucket",
      "â€¢ nats kv create almacen pala.troca grande",
      "â€¢ Setting a value",
      "â€¢ nats kv add almacen",
      "â€¢ nats kv create almacen pala.troca grande",
      "â€¢ Delete a key",
      "â€¢ nats kv del almacen pala.troca",
      "â€¢ Watch a store or key",
      "â€¢ nats kv watch almacen",
      "â€¢ nats kv watch almacen â€œpala.>â€",
      "![Page 38, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_038.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 39",
      "Object Store",
      "â€¢ Built on top of Jetstream",
      "â€¢ Builds a set of files or arbitrary size",
      "â€¢ An Object bucket corresponds to a stream",
      "â€¢ Operations on a bucket",
      "â€¢ put adds a file to a bucket",
      "â€¢ get retrieves a file and stores in a designated location",
      "â€¢ Stored as a collection of chunks",
      "â€¢ del removes a file",
      "â€¢ All files in a bucket must fit in a file system",
      "â€¢ Not a distributed storage system",
      "â€¢ watch informs of changes in a bucket",
      "![Page 39, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_039.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 40",
      "Example",
      "â€¢ Creating an Object Bucket",
      "â€¢ nats object put pueblo archie.zip",
      "â€¢ Storing a file",
      "â€¢ nats object add pueblo",
      "â€¢ nats object put â€“name archivo.zip pueblo archie.zip",
      "â€¢ Retrieving a file",
      "â€¢ nats object get pueblo archivo.zip",
      "â€¢ nats object get â€“output archie.zip pueblo archivo.zip",
      "![Page 40, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_040.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 41",
      "Q & A",
      "![Page 41, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/NATS-images/NATS_page_041.png)"
