      "â€¢Next: deï¬ne microservices precisely and contrast with distributed systems.â€¢Discuss organiza)onal and technical implica)ons.â€¢Iden)fy when NOT to adopt microservices.",
      "![Page 31, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_1_Introduction_Deck_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_1_Introduction_Deck_Bullets_Notes_page_031.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 32",
      "Discussion",
      "â€¢Where has a monolith been a bottleneck in your experience?â€¢Which domains would benefit most from independent deployments?",
      "![Page 32, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_1_Introduction_Deck_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_1_Introduction_Deck_Bullets_Notes_page_032.png)",
