      "### Page 18",
      "Public Cloud: Risks & Trade-Offs",
      "â€¢Shared tenancy and noisy-neighbor effects.â€¢Potential egress and premium managed-service costs.â€¢Compliance and data residency constraints.",
      "![Page 18, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_018.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 19",
      "Private Cloud: Definition & Benefits",
      "â€¢Dedicated infrastructure for one organization.â€¢Control, customization, and data locality.â€¢Predictable performance and governance.",
