      "",
      "### Page 20",
      "Private Cloud: Risks & Trade-Offs",
      "â€¢Higher capex and ops burden vs public cloud.â€¢Slower access to new managed services.â€¢Risk of under/over-provisioning capacity.",
      "![Page 20, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_020.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 21",
      "Hybrid Cloud: Definition & Benefits",
      "â€¢Combine public and private across one architecture.â€¢Burst capacity and place workloads where they fit.â€¢Data gravity respected; latency-sensitive parts stay close.",
      "![Page 21, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_021.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 22",
      "Hybrid Cloud: Risks & Trade-Offs",
      "â€¢Complex networking, identity, and policy management.â€¢Operational duplication across environments.â€¢Hidden latency and failure modes across links.",
      "![Page 22, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_022.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 23",
      "Community Cloud (Brief)",
      "â€¢Shared by organizations with common concerns.â€¢Often compliance-driven (sector-specific).â€¢Niche, but relevant in regulated domains.",
      "![Page 23, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_023.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 24",
      "Use Case: Web Applications",
      "â€¢Stateless tiers fit PaaS/serverless; databases managed.â€¢CDN, WAF, and auto-scaling patterns are common.â€¢Blue-green/canary releases reduce risk.",
      "![Page 24, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_024.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 25",
      "Use Case: Big Data & Analytics",
      "â€¢Object storage as data lake; serverless query engines.â€¢Batch and streaming pipelines (managed services).â€¢Governance: catalogs, lineage, access controls.",
      "![Page 25, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_025.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 26",
      "Use Case: AI/ML Workloads",
      "â€¢Managed notebooks, training, and inference endpoints.â€¢Access to accelerators (GPUs/TPUs) on demand.â€¢Feature stores and MLOps pipelines.",
      "![Page 26, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_026.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 27",
      "Use Case: Backup & DR",
      "â€¢Cross-region replication and immutable backups.â€¢Tiered storage classes to optimize cost.â€¢Test restores and document RTO/RPO.",
      "![Page 27, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_027.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 28",
      "Cloud Cost Models",
      "â€¢On-demand, reserved/committed use, and spot/preemptible.â€¢Per-request/serverless pricing vs provisioned capacity.â€¢Data egress and managed service premiums matter.",
      "![Page 28, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_028.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 29",
      "FinOps Basics",
      "â€¢Visibility: tagging, allocation, showback/chargeback.â€¢Optimization: rightsizing, autoscaling, schedules.â€¢Governance: budgets, alerts, guardrails.",
      "![Page 29, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_029.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 30",
      "Shared Responsibility Model",
      "â€¢Provider secures the cloud; you secure what you run.â€¢Responsibility shifts by service model (IaaSâ†’SaaS).â€¢Document controls: identity, network, data, app.",
      "![Page 30, Figure 1](subjects/Sad/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes-images/Session_3_Cloud_Service_Models_Bullets_Notes_page_030.png)",
      "",
      "### Page 31",
