      "â€¢ The basic architecture of a",
      "Transformer consists of two",
      "main parts:",
      "â€¢ the Encoder and",
      "â€¢ the Decoder",
      "â€¢ Each part is composed of a",
      "series of identical layers that",
      "process information",
