      "### Page 14",
      "Architecture of Transformers",
      "â€¢ Embeddings",
      "â€¢ Input Embedding: Converts the words in the input sequence into dense",
      "vectors that capture the meaning of each word.",
      "â€¢ Output Embedding: Similar to Input Embedding but for the output sequence.",
      "â€¢ Positional Encoding",
      "â€¢ Since Transformers do not process words sequentially, it is necessary to add",
      "information about the position of each word in the sequence.",
      "â€¢ This is achieved through Positional Encoding, which incorporates positional",
      "information into the embedding vectors.",
