      "â€¢ Cell state: Carries information through time",
      "2.LSTM Advantages for Speech",
      "â€¢ Handles variable-length sequences",
      "â€¢ Captures long-term dependencies",
      "â€¢ Resistant to vanishing gradients",
      "â€¢ Better at learning speech timing patterns",
      "â€¢ Maintains speaker context over time",
